summary: Novak Djokovic - Kei Nishikori (Head-to-Head) Novak will face Kei Nishikori in the quarter finals of the Australian Open on Rod...
caption:
Novak Djokovic - Kei Nishikori (Head-to-Head)

Novak will face Kei Nishikori in the quarter finals of the Australian Open on Rod Laver Arena on Wednesday at 7:30 PM local time (9:30 AM CET).

Novak has won their last 14 encounters. The last one was at the US Open last year where Novak beat Nishikori in straight sets.

(via atptour.com)
